commitResults.messageTitle: Add List and Mark as Done feature
commitResults.messageBody:
Implement the ability to add, list tasks and mark them as done.

The List feature allows users add tasks and view tasks they added.

The Mark as Done feature enables users to mark specific tasks as
completed. This improves user interaction by allowing them to keep
their task list up-to-date with their progress.

These features enhance the functionality of the chatbot.
